descriptionNullable:
This dataset is from a prominent state in India - Telangana. 
To know more on the number of states and mandals (sub-divisions in-state), refer [https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/List_of_mandals_of_Telangana](Wikipedia). 

All the features are self-explanatory. There is a lot of data cleaning involved and time-series analysis can be carried out! (But you are not limited to that alone 😉)

Upvote if you like this!

Taken from 
[https://data.telangana.gov.in/dataset/telangana-weather-data-2022](2022)
[https://data.telangana.gov.in/dataset/telangana-weather-data-2021](2021)
[https://data.telangana.gov.in/dataset/telangana-weather-data-2020](2020)
[https://data.telangana.gov.in/dataset/telangana-weather-data-2019](2019)
